        "product_description": {
            "value": "The ASR Tactical Kevlar Trip Wire delivers reliable performance for perimeter alarm setups and survival applications. This 85-foot spool of black, coated Kevlar wire offers an impressive 84-pound line strength while remaining lightweight and nearly invisible in the field. Made from durable Kevlar material, the trip wire resists stretching and abrasion, making it ideal for tripwire perimeter alarms, camping, survival kits, and outdoor security. Wound neatly on a convenient coil, it is easy to deploy and cut to your desired length. Backed by a limited lifetime manufacturer warranty, this versatile trip wire is a dependable addition to any tactical or survival gear collection.",
